abstract: >
  An enterprise-grade framework for enforcing data quality, governance,
  and observability across modern lakehouse architectures. This project
  introduces a unified approach integrating data contracts, policy-as-code,
  SLA monitoring, and audit-ready reporting for scalable data platforms.

